{
  "stem": "18520.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I worked there a little bit cleaning, bringing sand, doing this, this with everybody had to work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But later on, I got-- the first time, I got closer to the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the crematoriums-- the guys that were working-- they-- they couldn't-- nobody could talk to them because this was an isolated area.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The other guys?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, the guys that shoveled in the people?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, this is what they do-- they put them on this--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--this ledge.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the sliding in--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were taking the bodies out-- out of the crematorium?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, this-- the crematorium-- they were burned there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They lit all that was left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The bodies?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a mountain two stories high with dead people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were taking these bodies--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They die, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If then they didn't die, they poisoned them-- that's it-- to die.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They put them in the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had-- the-- the-- the gas chamber was so full, they couldn't make it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they poisoned people by drinking something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Burned them.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They couldn't burn them that much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, what they had there before-- when I left Auschwitz, I think they had, three stories high, a mountain of people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- I, you know-- you wanted to go to work because you knew, if you stay in the barrack, or you're not going, you're gone.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to pick up every day people they needed to burn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You better go to work and better not being sick.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sick people used to go till they couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what happened then is, they took me and other people to clean around the-- the gas chamber over there, not to have signs that people get the uprising before to see what's happening.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
